Function Reference/size format « WordPress Codex
-----------

Parameters
----------

 `$bytes` 
:   ([*mixed*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Mixed "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*required*) Number of bytes. Note max integer size for integers.
    Accepts int or string
    Default: *None*

 `$decimals` 
:   ([*int*](/How_to_Pass_Tag_Parameters#Int "How to Pass Tag Parameters"))
    (*optional*) Precision of number of decimal places. Deprecated.
    Default: 0

Return
------

boolean or string. False on failure. Number string on success.

Usage
-----

`  <?php  ?> `

